version_description: Added the Chords to the rest of the song. There are Chords in the later verses that aren't played at the beginning of the song and they weren't noted in other versions.
Provides simple chords for beginners and makes it a lot easy to worship than performing.
From 1990 version for piano which has guitar chords marked.
Full chord accompaniment for original song with some changes in chords, full realized at a lower tempo.
Song is in a different key with some chord variants changed and more chords added.
